(Your anonymous response to this question may be viewed by Yale College students, faculty, and advisers to aid in course selection and evaluating teaching.)
comments: I would definitely recommend this course. Alice is an amazing teacher and genuinely cares about giving feedback and supporting her students, the course is structured to help you evolve as a designer through enjoyable exercises and projects

Typography with Alice Chung was a great and fun class. She really dedicated a lot of time to the students and made sure that we all explored various facets of composition while encouraging us to put our own unique spin on our work.
Yes! Professor Chung was brilliant and so patient and dedicated to our learning!
